                    <span class="opener__topics ">
            <a class="opener__topics-link " href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/criminal-justice">Criminal Justice</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        Ticketed at School as a Teen, a Young Black Woman Is Suing an Illinois City for Violating Her Civil Rights
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " >        It took four years and a jury trial for Amara Harris to beat the ticket that accused her of stealing another girl’s AirPods. Now she’s heading back to court in the hope of stopping schools from using police to discipline students.
    </h2>

    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--left     " data-pp-location="article meta">

    <span class="article-meta-1__byline" data-pp-location="article byine">
